{"tid":189973,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"沖繩石恒十五日玩唔玩到","createTime":"2017-04-06T21:55:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-15T07:59:41.000Z","uid":6366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"62a7b7caac41d2cdc92a68facbdd2db36b42c982","tid":189973,"uid":6366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T21:55:40.000Z","msg":"買左沖繩去 石恒返機票<br />\n總共十五日<br />\n<br />\n時間應該點分配 內陸果程未買<br />\n搵過下石恒啲人話三四日己經開始悶 尤其自駕<br />\n<br />\n但本島十日又好似多得濟<br />\n<br />\n都係遇玩下水睇下景食下野潛水浮潛咁上下"},{"pid":"256e15a9a9f42a18f14b55ab82fccd337e4e048b","tid":189973,"uid":6366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T21:56:02.000Z","msg":"石垣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c979a6570e6ac3b5ca8740b7005b04a11aece3a4","tid":189973,"uid":2161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T22:01:21.000Z","msg":"15<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"236605893da46b00cd216cc4501565af425cb8ec","tid":189973,"uid":6366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T22:03:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>15<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咪長得濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cfd6f042e2e06b3bbec4f681c1e6185f39de72b","tid":189973,"uid":78376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T22:06:58.000Z","msg":"去過本島自駕5定6日唔記得咗，一定夠晒玩<br />\n你十幾日嘅話最好搵定啲local festival/隱蔽地方去吓。之前撞正有個打鼓跳舞festival同beer festival，雖然唔太震撼，但可以感受吓當地氣氛。<br />\n仲有有個係玩滑翔傘嘅叫sky-乜尻，可以一試<br />\n<br />\n石恒就真係冇去，因為之前睇見到好似比啲台灣人去到爛晒，加上景點同本島有好類似，所以嬲嬲哋唔去"},{"pid":"8989d6d8f56c5ea2701c0a84d95e45f34df0aed4","tid":189973,"uid":6366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T22:09:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去過本島自駕5定6日唔記得咗，一定夠晒玩<br />\n你十幾日嘅話最好搵定啲local festival/隱蔽地方去吓。之前撞正有個打鼓跳舞festival同beer festival，雖然唔太震撼，但可以感受吓當地氣氛。<br />\n仲有有個係玩滑翔傘嘅叫sky-乜尻，可以一試<br />\n<br />\n石恒就真係冇去，因為之前睇見到好似比啲台灣人去到爛晒，加上景點同本島有好類似，所以嬲嬲哋唔去</blockquote><br />\n因為石垣近台灣多過日本 台灣人好興去<br />\n但我買左石垣返既機票 所以點都會去 係分幾日時間姐<br />\n之前有巴打講過留左石垣八日 悶到嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eb6cf382241c137f1afe3ab812fc9b55ed1cf80","tid":189973,"uid":6366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T22:22:03.000Z","msg":"如果去下離島好似會好啲<br />\n<br />\n但係船費好貴同好小資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d1d8f6fd732926abe29ea58e6d94d9afb7c736f","tid":189973,"uid":6366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T00:47:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4e72867f645f32b8caecb3b7bb57bdcd03a9215","tid":189973,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T00:49:11.000Z","msg":"搵啲無人島自拍AV"},{"pid":"f9079cd46364379cc0ec12d8c5808843948401ab","tid":189973,"uid":10905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T00:55:36.000Z","msg":"點解仲有咁多人去石垣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d535312df12c07043decdc470214f7dbc88d2a59","tid":189973,"uid":6366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T00:59:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搵啲無人島自拍AV</blockquote><br />\n巴打有無無人島推介<br />\n游下裸泳都好"},{"pid":"4dee8b6ebff7a85056419a52283a8905b6880dbf","tid":189973,"uid":6366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T00:59:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解仲有咁多人去石垣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n廉航有航線嘛"},{"pid":"3c11b5a8a5f2048fbd76ff630fe820946dbd67ca","tid":189973,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T01:07:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解仲有咁多人去石垣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解你咁講？因為冇嘢玩？<br />\n定核廢料？"},{"pid":"04e93f8cc9667f4995dfddaca4b801f5641b296f","tid":189973,"uid":6366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T02:06:39.000Z","msg":"旅遊台沈得咁快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e9314610a02bf2854d6af10f4746986ff7ce5a8","tid":189973,"uid":50909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T02:08:08.000Z","msg":"我前年去沖繩8日自駕遊就岩岩好"},{"pid":"0b69fcec331915a25d566224b5345890e0d6e3e2","tid":189973,"uid":6366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T02:18:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我前年去沖繩8日自駕遊就岩岩好</blockquote><br />\n巴打係玩晒成個沖繩？<br />\n有無覺得邊到值得stay耐啲"},{"pid":"b018d6a1e91891390ffbf412f1dacb1aa354a06c","tid":189973,"uid":98891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T02:54:31.000Z","msg":"石垣潛水超正"},{"pid":"244aad4beaf83a3e457c5f3d75365b2ef9c66cd5","tid":189973,"uid":6366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T02:57:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>石垣潛水超正</blockquote><br />\n因為本島果邊都會潛<br />\n我預去石垣潛一日咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定還是好多潛點值多潛多幾鑊<br />\n<br />\n岩岩先諗緊如果plan完太多時間剩去抽兩日考埋aow去"},{"pid":"2614cf8998446a06687bef581dcea6be750adf70","tid":189973,"uid":6366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T09:14:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>石垣潛水超正</blockquote><br />\n因為本島果邊都會潛<br />\n我預去石垣潛一日咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定還是好多潛點值多潛多幾鑊<br />\n<br />\n岩岩先諗緊如果plan完太多時間剩去抽兩日考埋aow去</blockquote><br />\n問左間話旺季唔開班 笑左"},{"pid":"2cfa04e700ae7489f93502002974031112d3264a","tid":189973,"uid":6366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T11:12:13.000Z","msg":"推下先"},{"pid":"ecbb4925949b7cb961f2ff895ec8dbe5b6ac1baa","tid":189973,"uid":6366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T16:38:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"282cadf902c3127ca3bd402cd0619a361546dfda","tid":189973,"uid":6366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T00:20:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbb2982458864f1c1702f7b5b5e897833182cccb","tid":189973,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T00:21:28.000Z","msg":"十五日 享受人生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a26e7392dbc7d3c3e5dd8780fe2cde866ea0f50","tid":189973,"uid":88301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T07:12:25.000Z","msg":"小弟15年去沖繩石垣9日，起石垣留咗三四日左右，你十五日最好就去一兩個外島啦，始終石垣好快遊曬，沖繩又景點有限，十五日會有d辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"548da072f9651c5622ed53751a3e83417b37e0a5","tid":189973,"uid":59666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T07:54:09.000Z","msg":"我去過十幾廿日<br />\nplan多d外島 多多期都唔夠你玩<br />\n外島 &gt;石垣&gt;沖繩<br />\n外島2/3 石垣+沖繩1/3"}]}